Package store.business.gui.controller

Class NewClientController

  • java.lang.Object
    • store.business.gui.controller.NewClientController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    public class NewClientController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable

    The Controller for creating a new client

    The public class NewClientController class implements the public interface Initializable interface in order to unfocus all the components of the view and to add a listener on each Input Text to disable/enable the submit button

    1.0.0

    Author:
